content: Hi, I just checked my autograder grade for pset 4 and it says 28% even though my code passes all the test cases. Why is this?
subject: autograder 28% when I passed all the test cases

content:
Hi Stella,

The server test cases differ from those in the student tester file. For example, in testing dataset loading, we expect your code to extract columns other than "Close", as described in the pset description and function docstring. However, your code has hardcoded a particular column to extract.

Hope that helps,

Matt
